Given an embedding `e` of complex shapes that satisfies `IsTruncGE`, we show that the morphism `K.Ï€TruncGE e : K âŸ¶ K.truncGE e` induces a quasi-isomorphism in degree `e.f i` for all `i`.

---

This PR shall be further split into two: one for the additions to the general homology API, and one specific to `truncGE`.

- [ ] depends on: #19570
- [ ] depends on: #19544
- [ ] depends on: #19543
- [ ] depends on: #19203
- [ ] depends on: #18502
- [ ] depends on: #19198
